JEFFERY RICHARDSON, A/K/A JEFFERY OSBORNE RICHARDSON, JEFFREY RICHARDSON, JEFFERY O. RICHARDSON, JEFFREY RICHRARDSON, DEFENDANT.

C-418 September Term 2017

079661 December 8, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-4021/4026-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;
